window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Caelum: an Academy built to protect people like Eve. Who they can't protect her from? Its own student body.</p> <p>The threat of death isn't new to Eve, but when she's given the chance to escape her past, she prays her future will be brighter. How wrong she is.</p> <p>Raised in a cult, Eve has no understanding of the modern world. Targeted as a freak, a Pack of boys take her under their wing but one among them recognizes Eve for what she is. Trouble. And a threat.</p> <p>At Caelum, threats need eliminating....</p> <p>Eve survived her past, but what of her future?</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
